description: Removes one or more tags (keys and values) from an Amazon Macie resource.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: One or more tags (keys) to remove from the resource. In an HTTP request to remove multiple tags, append the tagKeys parameter and argument for each tag to remove, separated by an ampersand (&). (string) ---
